==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Gritty
<hw>Grit"ty</hw> <pr>(-t⟦ycr⟧)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Containing sand or grit; consisting of grit; caused by grit; full
of hard particles.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Spirited; resolute; unyielding.</def>
<mark>[Colloq., U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Grivet</ent>⟦br⟧
